"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-news-uk-paris-olympics-french-eurotunnel-eurostar-b2586443.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Sports fans travelling by train toParisfor theOlympicsopening ceremony have had their plans thrown into jeopardy by arson attacks on theFrenchrail network.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurostarhas advised customers to postpone their trips if they can and said it will cancel 25% of trains on Friday and over the weekend, but there are several other ways to reach the French capital.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9593738060921398, \"rank\": 0.04145208567518123, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here the PA news agency looks at four alternative ways stranded passengers can get to Paris.\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982348982, \"rank\": 1.7651730901740238e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Drive  While travelling by rail may not be an option, drivers can still make it in time for the start of the Games.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Drivers will need to reach Calais in northern France by ferry orEurotunnel, before re-joining the road for the approximately three-and-a-half-hour drive to Paris.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"score\": 0.9926584019042874, \"rank\": 0.007395895790160921, \"text\": \"Calais\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995911620114052, \"rank\": 0.0002148305658904365, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982348982, \"rank\": 1.7651730901740238e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cheapest P&O ferry leaving Dover on Friday costs \\u00a3149 and arrives into Calais at 8.05pm, so punters will have to purchase a more expensive ticket if they want to reach Paris before the ceremony begins at 7.30pm.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Dover\", \"score\": 0.9583972378675492, \"rank\": 0.04340868324405546, \"text\": \"Dover\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Dover\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Dover\"}, {\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"score\": 0.9926584019042874, \"rank\": 0.007395895790160921, \"text\": \"Calais\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982348982, \"rank\": 1.7651730901740238e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eurotunnel is offering all standard crossings from Folkestone at \\u00a3248, with the earliest available reaching Calais at 2.53pm.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\", \"score\": 0.9916982461586993, \"rank\": 0.00837124989739598, \"text\": \"Eurotunnel\", \"types\": [\"Q1311958\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_Tunnel\"}, {\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"score\": 0.9926584019042874, \"rank\": 0.007395895790160921, \"text\": \"Calais\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_of_Calais\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Coach  Coach travel will most likely be the cheapest way to reach Paris.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982348982, \"rank\": 1.7651730901740238e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flixbus is offering direct coaches from Stratford and Greenwich for \\u00a3193, but available seats are selling fast and both options arrive in Paris past midnight.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flixbus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flixbus\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flixbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flixbus\"}, {\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford_station\", \"score\": 0.9999557405726107, \"rank\": 2.6242653341969397e-05, \"text\": \"Stratford\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stratford_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich\", \"score\": 0.9993348491398056, \"rank\": 0.000665589105948762, \"text\": \"Greenwich\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenwich\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982348982, \"rank\": 1.7651730901740238e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While you could catch the first day of medal events, this is not an option for those with plans to watch the Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.993463563137638, \"rank\": 0.00505600097464283, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Fly  According to Skyscanner, there are no direct flights available on Friday from London or Manchester to Paris, so fans will have to wait until Saturday for their earliest chance to reach the French capital.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1811, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skyscanner\",